er and Student Center West. Conveniently located near health professions colleges, UIC Shuttle service and the Pink and Blue line are just two blocks away.  Plus, we organize and offer great opportunities such as networking events with other students and faculty in your field, so all you have to do is focus on your studies.      Full Academic Year  Apply Here!      Medical Rotation     We know Medical Students have different needs for their living environment, which sometimes includes shorter stays. We are able to accommodate for these rotations in SSR.  In Campus Housing, we want to make your stay enjoyable and as convenient as possible to help you succeed.    Length of Stay  Weekly Rate      1-3 weeks  $250    4-6 weeks  $230    7-9 weeks  $210    10-36 weeks  $200         Medical Rotation  Apply Here!       Additional Comments   Please indicate in the Additional Comments section that you are on Medical Rotation to receive these special rates.          GUESTS AND CONFERENCES    Back to main content           Guest Housing    Medical Students    Intern Housing    Conference Housing     Resources                    UIC Logo        Campus Housing         Future    Apply    Housing Rates    Residence Halls    Services    Why Live on Campus      Current    Apply    Summer Housing    Housing During Breaks    Academic Support    Get Involved    Services      GUESTS AND CONFERENCES    Conference Housing    Guest Housing    Intern Housing    Medical Students        Button Menu    Dates to Know    Contact Us    Dock    MyContract    Student Affairs         Contact   818 S. Wolcott Ave., Suite 220, Chicago IL 60612  Phone: 312-355-6300  Fax: 312-355-6304  housing@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affair